            . I live in <placeName id="t18180401-181-crimeloc1029">Duke-street, Bloomsbury</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18180401-181-crimeloc1029" type="placeName" value="Duke-street, Bloomsbury"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18180401-181-crimeloc1029" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180401-181-off1027 t18180401-181-crimeloc1029"></join>. My watch hung on the shelf in my parlour. I was cleaning my door-step, the prisoner passed me, and went up the street, while I was cleaning my railing - He ran in and came out. I tried to stop him in my passage - He threw me down and got off; I am sure he is the boy. I missed my watch - He was taken eight days after.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18180401-181-person1300">
